headline.main: 9-1 BASSANIO WINS $58,800 MONMOUTH; Beats Closed Door With Fast Stretch Run in Handicap -- Level Lea Is Third

results.lead_paragraph: OCEANPORT, N. J., July 24 -- Ogden Phipps' Bassanio won the $58,800 Monmouth Handicap today. The 4-year-old colt, a son of Bimelech, was kept in a challenging position through most of the mile and a quarter test by Sid Cole, and in the stretch he turned on the speed enough to finish first by more than two lengths.
